T1  - An age profile perspective on two puzzles in global child health: The Indian Enigma & economic growth
AU  - Aiyar, Anaka
AU  - Cummins, Joseph R.
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 148
SP  - 102569
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/01/01/
SN  - 0304-3878
